Shahnez Boushaki (Ọktoba 22, 1985, Algiers) bụ onye egwuregwu basketball nke Algeria nke na-agba bọọlụ Mouloudia Club nke Algiers, Ụlọ ọrụ Club Petroleum Sports Group na otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị Algeria.
Boushaki gbara egwuregwu oge asatọ maka Mouloudia Club nke Algiers (MCA) kemgbe 2002, wee kpuchie oge izizi ya ebe ahụ.
Ọ malitere ọrụ ọkachamara ya na GS Pétroliers nke Algerian Women's Basketball Cup na 2010
Boushaki meriri asọmpi basketball nke ụmụ nwanyị Algeria na 2015 ya na ndị otu ya GS Pétroliers bụ ndị meriri ndị ha na ha na-asọmpi Olympic Club nke Algiers na egwuregwu ikpeazụ na akara 73-55.
Ya na ndị otu GS Pétroliers sonyela n'ọtụtụ asọmpi basketball n'ime usoro nke Arab Club Basketball Championship, ya bụ:
Boushaki bụ onye otu egwuregwu basketball nke mba Algeria kemgbe afọ 2010
N'afọ 2017, ọ bụ onye otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Algeria nke ruru eru maka asọmpi iko FIBA Africa Iko iko bọọlụ ụmụnwaanyị Afrịka.
